## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ’¬ Natural language understanding (NLU)-based chatbot
- ğŸ“Š Covers topics like:
  - Stock prices and market hours
  - Investment vs. trading
  - Portfolio building and diversification
  - Risk management and stop-loss
  - Dividends and income investing
- ğŸ¯ Easy to extend with more intents (like crypto, mutual funds, etc.)
- ğŸ“± Interactive and user-friendly UI built with Streamlit

